  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at level 7, you become incredibly resilient, as though you have multiple lives. <br />Whenever you would drop to 0 HP, you instead drop to 1 HP once per long rest (unless you are killed outright). <br />Additionally, once per month, if you would die, you instead become stable. <br />Starting at level 11, when you would drop to 0 HP you instead recover 1/4 of your max HP (instead of the original 1 HP). </p>",
